<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 21:12:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>流亡中国商人郭在美国欺诈审判中被判有罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/jury-reaches-verdict-exiled-chinese-businessman-guos-us-fraud-trial-2024-07-16/</link><description>郭文贵是一位流亡的中国商人，也是北京共产党政府的直言不讳的反对者，周二在美国的审判中被判有罪，罪名是从网上追随者那里窃取数亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 19:22:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/jury-reaches-verdict-exiled-chinese-businessman-guos-us-fraud-trial-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>戴姆勒卡车因中国市场疲软而出现减值</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/daimler-truck-reports-12-bln-operating-profit-2024-07-16/</link><description>戴姆勒卡车周二表示，由于中国“市场持续疲软”，该公司将在第二季度对其在华合资企业的价值进行减值，并补充说其全年指引正在“审查中”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 18:25:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/daimler-truck-reports-12-bln-operating-profit-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国支出减少拖累欧洲奢侈品股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-reduced-spending-saps-european-luxury-stocks-2024-07-16/</link><description>Hugo Boss 的盈利预警和历峰集团 (Richemont) 在中国的疲弱销售进一步证明中国人对奢侈品的需求可能已经达到顶峰，从而打压了周二的股价，而保时捷在全球第二大经济体中的投资也令投资者感到不安。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:36:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-reduced-spending-saps-european-luxury-stocks-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，欧盟国家在投票中对中国电动汽车关税存在分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-members-give-mixed-view-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-sources-say-2024-07-16/</link><description>了解投票情况的消息人士周二表示，欧盟各国政府在一次不具约束力但仍有影响力的投票中，就欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车进口关税的优点提出了分歧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:33:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-members-give-mixed-view-vote-chinese-ev-tariffs-sources-say-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>数字平台 Qifa 押注俄中贸易和支付的增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/digital-platform-qifa-bets-increase-russia-china-trade-payments-2024-07-16/</link><description>数字平台 Qifa 已扩展到促进俄罗斯和中国之间的双向贸易，以解决目前阻碍商品和服务流动的支付问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:21:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/digital-platform-qifa-bets-increase-russia-china-trade-payments-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，欧盟可能降低大众和宝马的中国电动汽车进口关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brussels-may-rethink-china-ev-import-tariffs-volkswagen-bmw-sources-say-2024-07-16/</link><description>两位知情人士称，欧盟委员会已向大众汽车和宝马发出信号，可能考虑降低这两家汽车制造商进口中国制造的电动汽车的关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 14:48:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brussels-may-rethink-china-ev-import-tariffs-volkswagen-bmw-sources-say-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>芬兰在周一欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税的投票中投了弃权票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/finland-abstained-mondays-vote-eu-tariffs-china-evs-2024-07-16/</link><description>芬兰驻欧盟大使馆的一名官员周二表示，芬兰在周一欧盟就中国制造的电动汽车临时关税进行的投票中投了弃权票。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 13:33:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/finland-abstained-mondays-vote-eu-tariffs-china-evs-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国紫金矿业拟收购加拿大澜起黄金9.9%股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-zijin-mining-take-99-stake-canadas-montage-gold-2024-07-16/</link><description>加拿大矿业公司蒙太奇黄金公司周二表示，中国矿业公司紫金矿业集团将通过私募方式获得该公司 9.9% 的战略股权。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 13:30:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-zijin-mining-take-99-stake-canadas-montage-gold-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>贸易机构负责人表示，台湾企业将供应链从中国转移到印度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-firms-shift-supply-chains-india-china-trade-body-chief-says-2024-07-16/</link><description>台湾主要贸易机构负责人告诉路透社，随着主要经济体之间的全球贸易紧张局势加剧，台北和新德里加强了经济联系，台湾企业正在将供应链从中国转移到印度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:55:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-firms-shift-supply-chains-india-china-trade-body-chief-says-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，普华永道考虑将中国金融服务审计人员减半</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-weighs-halving-china-financial-services-audit-staff-say-sources-2024-07-16/</link><description>两名知情人士表示，普华永道 (PwC) 正在考虑将其在中国的金融服务审计人员削减至多一半，原因是监管调查和客户流失使业务前景黯淡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-weighs-halving-china-financial-services-audit-staff-say-sources-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国国有券商将扩大在东南亚的投资银行业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-state-owned-brokerage-ramp-up-investment-banking-business-southeast-asia-2024-07-16/</link><description>国有券商中国银河证券 (CGS) 的一名高级管理人员表示，计划明年将其在东南亚的投资银行团队从目前的 30 人扩大到 50 人，并押注在市场低迷的情况下该地区的交易量会增加在家里。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:09:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-state-owned-brokerage-ramp-up-investment-banking-business-southeast-asia-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行聘请前英国政治家领导新基础设施部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/hsbc-launches-new-climate-focused-infrastructure-finance-unit-2024-07-16/</link><description>一位高级银行高管告诉路透社，英国汇丰银行已成立一个新部门，以挖掘与世界向低碳经济转型相关的基础设施融资和项目融资交易，并聘请了一位前英国政治家来领导该部门。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/hsbc-launches-new-climate-focused-infrastructure-finance-unit-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>对于全球投资者来说，中国是一个缓慢燃烧的贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-investors-china-is-slow-burning-trade-2024-07-16/</link><description>对于在中国股市持有资金的全球投资者来说，最新的经济数据并没有带来任何安慰，只是提醒他们，他们所押注的复苏需要一段时间才能实现。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 06:31:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-investors-china-is-slow-burning-trade-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国需求疲软损害了奢侈品公司历峰集团的销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-says-quarterly-sales-up-1-constant-exchange-rates-2024-07-16/</link><description>卡地亚母公司历峰集团周二表示，截至 6 月份的三个月内，该奢侈品集团的销售额几乎持平，中国需求下滑导致整体业绩略低于预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:47:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-says-quarterly-sales-up-1-constant-exchange-rates-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国计划煤电行业低碳升级</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plans-low-carbon-upgrades-coal-power-sector-2024-07-16/</link><description>中国计划通过试点使用煤炭与绿色氨或生物质混合的电厂燃烧以及碳捕获、利用和封存来减少煤电行业的碳排放。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:22:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plans-low-carbon-upgrades-coal-power-sector-2024-07-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>